        <mxCell id="BbdwhsDY87xifgJ9cqkn-8" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;spacingLeft=8;fillColor=#ffffff;fontColor=#000000;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1.5;" value="&lt;b&gt;Lesson 04: Kiểu dữ liệu cơ bản&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Số nguyên (int):&lt;/b&gt; 5, -12&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Số thực (float):&lt;/b&gt; 3.14, -0.5&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Chuỗi ký tự (str):&lt;/b&gt; &quot;Hello&quot;, &#39;Python&#39;&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Logic (bool):&lt;/b&gt; True hoặc False&lt;br&gt;👉 Hàm kiểm tra kiểu dữ liệu: &lt;i&gt;type()&lt;/i&gt;" vertex="1">
